				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Mages get 2-4 bind points and individual spells to gate to each point.  2-3 sec.  gate (self-summon) cast time.  Reasonable mana usage, on the order of a typical stun spell.
<br />

<br />
1.  Allows CotH to be somewhat usefull, in comparision to totally useless as it is now.
<br />
2.  Enables an intelligent PvPer, with time to survey and setup, to pull off some wins.
<br />
3.  Gives us a damage-avoidance ability somewhat similar to snare-(kiting).
<br />
4.  Compliments our long range bolt nukes very nicely.
<br />

<br />
It wouldn't allow us to do anything a snare-kiter can't do against, say, mobs that summon.
<br />

<br />
Thoughts?  Any obvious exploits?
<br />

<br />
I would also like some very mana efficient fast-cast nukes.  Expand the scars of sigil line pls!
<br />

<br />
Anyways, after a cpl years of lurking and then trolling I thought I'd post something which migh possibly be usefull.<br />_________________<br />Stone Cutters
<br />
Federation of Povar</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
